Shipping And Warranty

  • All orders will contain a copy of the customer's purchase receipt as well as the products.
  • During regular working days, all customer orders have a 6-hour window to modify their shipping information.
  • Customers can cancel orders placed during regular business hours (Monday through Friday) within 12 hours. Please send an email to support@bodywell.com requesting cancellation.
  • Customers who submit orders over the weekend or on holidays can cancel them within 24 hours. The request will be handled the following business day. Please send an email to support@bodywell.com requesting cancellation.
  • During regular working days, all customer purchases will be processed and sent within a 24-hour window, with the exception of weekends, holidays, or unanticipated occurrences.
  • Customers in Canada and the United States should expect to receive their packages within 5 business days of purchasing.
  • If an item is ordered and then becomes backordered or out of stock, Bodywell® will send the quantity of the order that is currently in stock. When the item becomes available, Bodywell® will ship the remaining items in your purchase, and you will not be charged any additional shipping or related expenses. Bodywell® will make every effort to deliver any product that is temporarily out of stock or on back order as quickly as possible.
  • All customer support inquiries will be responded to during regular business hours or the following business day (24hrs).

Customer Tracking and Order Responsibilities

  • When a customer's order is complete, they will receive an email confirmation that their order has been processed and shipped, along with their tracking number.

NOTE: It's possible that tracking information won't be accessible until after the carrier has picked up the package.
